                '(some-emacs-wiki-variable . "some-emacs-wiki-value"))
   (planner-option-customized 'planner-custom-variables
                              planner-custom-variables)
@end example

See @code{emacs-wiki-update-project} and @code{planner-custom-variables} for more
details.

